Alewife habitat

habitat_ale.Rd

A dataset containing the surface area of Alewife habitat segments by feature (dam or outlet) in Atlantic coast drainages.

Usage

habitat_ale

Format

A data frame with 246,259 observations of 26 variables:

Names NEED TO ADD DESCRIPTIONS

Source

Shawn Snyder

Examples

print(habitat_ale)
